{"tid":2335714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑客組織取得　中國網信辦文件　揭露中國政府如何操縱疫情輿論","createTime":"2020-12-22T05:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T07:17:25.000Z","uid":261647,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ab9c195a899743171d1b58857b254896aad99c","tid":2335714,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:33:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417296&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=4bfd4fd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417296&h=fbb852fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417296</a><br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》和獨立傳媒引述中國官方文件，揭露自年初爆發新冠疫情，當局如何操縱網絡輿論，壓制負面新聞，包括吹哨人李文亮醫生的死訊，以重新掌握話語權。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》和專門調查報道的獨立傳媒ProPublica取得來自名為「揭秘中共」的黑客組織，和追蹤中國網絡監控的「中國數位時代」網站提供的文件，包括中共中央網絡安全和信息化委員會辦公室，簡稱網信辦杭州辦事處的3200多條指示、1800多份備忘錄，及開發軟件協助監控網絡討論的雲潤大數據內部文件和電腦代碼，詳細揭露中國政府在新冠疫情期間如何操縱輿論。<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示今年一月，內地出現不明肺炎個案，網信辦要求內地傳媒不可與沙士疫情相提並論，二月再發指示稱，不僅要控制國內信息，還要「積極影響國際輿論」，不使用「無法治癒」、「致命」、「封鎖」等字眼，不要大肆渲染海外捐贈和購買醫療用品的報道。<br />\n<br />\n被視為疫情吹哨人的內地醫生李文亮染疫死亡後，當局下達秘密指示，警告他的死帶來「前所未有的挑戰」，可能引發蝴蝶效應，官員必須努力壓制負面新聞，重新掌握話語權，命令新聞網站不要將李文亮死訊推送給讀者，要求社交平台逐步將他的名字由熱門搜尋話題頁面移除。<br />\n<br />\n當局又發動大量虛假的網絡評論員，分散注意力，指示嚴肅制止和處理藉此事煽動輿論情緒的內容，之後大量網上紀念活動消失，有人被捕。"},{"pid":"ca3393456ad376cf5ce4a05dad847dd3602f834c","tid":2335714,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c3bdc52cdb65efe16a6337f783b2c2ed4c88a7","tid":2335714,"uid":11809,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋進化咗，我哋仲喺度分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833084868b322dc198ba139f45a7cd8a102370fe","tid":2335714,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"a3a77541e22bc9b7f0879533b789a700e533f2d5","tid":2335714,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:41:38.000Z","msg":"國安仲唔派香港警察去拉人？<br />\n支持香港警察"},{"pid":"ca80f6855d6d7c75cb5120c733f0df30fe71fe00","tid":2335714,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef0c114e762b9405fa9df7da4f0bbaa0633c02c","tid":2335714,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29c3bdc52cdb65efe16a6337f783b2c2ed4c88a7","tid":2335714,"uid":11809,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋進化咗，我哋仲喺度分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"連登大把呢D柒頭"},{"pid":"41b6679f057bb8d9bf037fab94091ac59c323319","tid":2335714,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29c3bdc52cdb65efe16a6337f783b2c2ed4c88a7","tid":2335714,"uid":11809,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋進化咗，我哋仲喺度分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfb958d8d052ffcf429ed1e57f06fff246f1d36","tid":2335714,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"中國維穩世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7e2c8dfc44b196ebc4a8